quran[60]{c,v,t}:
  51,1,Mede (mframa den a) etu mfutro hwete
  51,2,Ne mununkum a εsoa nsuo a emu yε duro
  51,3,Ne nsuom hyεn a εnam po so bͻkͻͻ
  51,4,"Ne (Soro abͻfoͻ) no a wͻ’kyekyε ahyεdeε no, di nse sε"
  51,5,"Ampa, deε yahyε mo ho bͻ no yε nokorε paa"
  51,6,Nokorε nso sε Akatua (da) no besi
  51,7,Mede ͻsoro a akwan ahodoͻ wͻ mu no di nse sε
  51,8,"“Nokorε sε, mowͻ nsεm sononko-sononko (na moka fa Nkͻmhyεni ne Qur’aan ho)"
  51,9,Obi a wayera na ͻdane neho (fri Nokorε no ho no) dane neho fri ho
  51,10,"Due nka wͻn a wͻ’bͻ wͻn trim twa, nkontompo no"
  51,11,Wͻn a wͻn wͻ anibianaso ne awerεfire mu no
  51,12,"Wͻ’bisa (dedi fεw) sε: “Ɛberε bεn ne Owusͻreε da no?’’"
  51,13,Ɛne Ɛda no a yεbεsͻ wͻn ahwε anaasε yεbεhyε wͻn aniεyaa wͻ Ogya no mu no
  51,14,"(Yε’bεka akyerε wͻn sε): “ Monka monsͻhwε no a na morepε no ntεm no nhwε“"
  51,15,Nokorε sε Nyame-surofoͻ no wͻ Soro aheman no ne nsuo aniwa mu
  51,16,Wͻ’regye deε wͻn Wura Nyankopͻn dema wͻn no. Nokorε sε kane no na wͻ’yε ayεmyεfoͻ
  51,17,Na (εberε) ketewaabi na na wͻ’de da wͻ anadwo
  51,18,Na ahomakye no wͻ’de srε (Nyankopͻn hͻ) bͻnefakyε
  51,19,Na adesrεfoͻ ne ahiafoͻ wͻ kyεfa wͻ wͻn agyapadeε mu
  51,20,Nsεnkyerεnee (pii) wͻ asaase so dema wͻn a wͻ’agye die no
  51,21,Ɛne mo nipa dua no mu nso; enti mo nnhunu anaa
  51,22,Ɔsoro na moakͻnhoma ne deε yahyε mo ho bͻ no wͻ
  51,23,"Enti Mede ͻsoro ne asaase Wura no di nse sε, (deε yahyε mo ho bͻ no) yε nokorε sεdeε morekasa no ara pεpεεpε"
  51,24,Enti Abraham ahͻhoͻ nimuonyamfoͻ no ho asεm no abeduru wo hͻ
  51,25,"Ɛberε a wͻ’baa nehͻ no, wͻ’kaa sε: “‘Salaam’ Asomdwiε nka wo“.(Abraham nso) kaa sε: “Salaam: Asomdwiε nka mo”; moyε ahͻhoͻ a yenni mo"
  51,26,Enti ͻdanee neho kͻͻ nefiefoͻ hͻ de nantwie a wadͻre nam a yahoͻ (anaasε yatotoo) bae
  51,27,"Ɔde besii wͻn anim kaa sε: ”Adεn monnidi?”"
  51,28,"Enti onyaa wͻn ho suro bi. (Abͻfoͻ no) kaa sε: “Ensuro! Wͻ’de abarimaa nimdefoͻ bi (Is’haaq) hyεε no bͻ “"
  51,29,"Abraham yere (Saratu) de nteamu fri bae, na ͻbͻͻ (ͻno ara) aniso kaa sε: Aberewa bonini"
  51,30,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Saa ara na wo Wura Nyankopͻn aka. Nokorε sε Ɔne Onyansafoͻ no, Ɔne Onimdefoͻ no"
  51,31,"Abraham kaa sε: “Asomafoͻ, na mo amaneε paa ne sεn?”"
  51,32,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Y’asoma yεn wͻ amanfoͻ nnebͻneεfoͻ bi hͻ"
  51,33,Sε yεnkͻto aboͻ a yεde nεteε a yatoo na ayε ngu wͻn so
  51,34,(Aboͻ a yεde nεteε a yato na ayε a) yahyε no nso fri wo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ dema abͻneεfoͻ no (a obiara din wͻ nedeε soͻ)“
  51,35,Enti Yeyii obiara a na ͻyε gyedieni frii mu
  51,36,Na Y’annya efie biara gyesε (efie) baako pε na na εyε Muslimifoͻ (fie)
  51,37,Enti Ye’gyaa nsεnkyerεnee wͻ hͻ maa wͻn a wͻ’suro asotwee yaaya no
  51,38,"Mose hͻ nso, εberε a Yε’de nyinasoͻ pefee somaa no kͻͻ Farao hͻ"
  51,39,"Nanso (Farao) de neho too netumi so kaa sε: “Nkoyaayini anaasε ͻbͻdamfoͻ”"
  51,40,"Enti Yε’pari sͻͻ ͻne nedͻm no mu, na Yε’de wͻn guu ͻpo mu; na ͻyε obi a ͻfata soboͻ"
  51,41,"Aadfoᴐ no hᴐ nso , εberε a Yε’somaa mframa nini no baa wͻn soͻ"
  51,42,"Adeε biara nnihͻ a εtoo no na egyaee no, na mmom ebubuu mu yεε no muhumuhu tesε nsoo (anaa kasεε a ahunu)"
  51,43,"Samuudfoͻ no hͻ nso; εberε a yεka kyerεε wͻn sε: “Modeε monye moani nkosi εberε bi “"
  51,44,Nanso wͻ’tee wͻn Wura Nyankopͻn ahyεdeε no so atua. Enti nteamu asotwee no sͻͻ wͻn mu aberε a na wͻn ani tua
  51,45,"Wͻ’antumi ansͻre anyina (wͻn nan so), na wͻ’antumi ammoa wͻn ho nso"
  51,46,Noa nkorͻfoͻ na wͻ’dii kan; na wͻ’yε nnipa nsεmͻnedifoͻ
  51,47,"Yε’de Yetumi na esii ͻsoro no, na nokorε sε, Yεn ara na Yε’bae (ͻsoro) ntrεmu no mu"
  51,48,Ɛna Yε’de asaase no nso asε hͻ; na sεdeε Y’asi atrε mu yie paa
  51,49,Adeε biara no Ya’bͻ no mmienu mmienu (onini ne ͻbedeε) sεdeε mobεkaeε
  51,50,Enti monwane nkͻ mo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ. Nokorε sε meyε kͻkͻbͻni pefee fri Nehͻ mamo
  51,51,"Na monhwε na moanyε awurade foforͻ biara anka Nyankopͻn ho. Nokorε sε, meyε kͻkͻbͻni pefee fri Nehͻ mamo"
  51,52,"Saa ara nso na Asomafoͻ a wͻ’baa amanfoͻ a wͻ’dii wͻn anim kan no hͻ no, wͻ’ka kyerεε wͻn sε wͻ’yε nkoyaayifoͻ anaasε wͻn abobͻ adam"
  51,53,"(Tetefoͻ no) na wͻ’tuu wͻn fo saa anaa? Daabi, wͻn ara yε nnipa a wͻ’to mmara"
  51,54,"Enti twe woho fri wͻn ho, na yεmmͻ wo soboͻ"
  51,55,"Na tufo, efrisε afutuo no ho wͻ mfasoͻ ma agyidiefoͻ no"
  51,56,"Ɛnyε hwee ho nti na Mebͻͻ Jinn ne nnipa, na mmom (Mebͻͻ wͻn) sε wͻ’nsom Me"
  51,57,"Mennhwehwε akͻnhoma biara wͻ wͻn hͻ, na mennhwehwε nso sε wͻ’ma Me biribi nni"
  51,58,"Nokorε sε, Nyankopͻn ne Ɔkyε adeε Hene; Otumfoͻ Ɔhoͻdenfoͻ paa ne no"
  51,59,"Nokorε sε, wͻn a wͻ’di bͻne no wͻ bͻne so asotwee tesε wͻn a wͻ’dii kan wͻ wͻn anim no ara pεpεεpε; enti εmma wͻn mpre ho sε Memfa (asotwee no) mmra"
  51,60,Enti due nka wͻn a wͻ’po (nokorε) no wͻ wͻn Da a yahyε wͻn ho bͻ no mu